title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Om Mangalam Mangalam
subTitle: A woman becomes mesmerised by a man's singing, unaware of his criminal side. However, when she loses her eyesight in a serious accident, he takes care of her and falls for her.

title: Ghar Mein Ram Gali Mein Shyam
subTitle: Amar weds a village belle and they move to the city where she meets her neighbours Mr and Mrs Dharamchand. Soon, Amar begins to doubt her fidelity and Dharamchand devises a scheme to separate them.

title: Aasman Se Ooncha
subTitle: Inspector Malik transfers to Mumbai along with his family and sets out on a mission to catch King, an underworld leader. However, a shocking revelation changes the course of their lives.

title: Kaun Kare Kurbanie
subTitle: Arjun Singh, a police inspector, lives peacefully with his family in Mumbai, until an alarming case of harassment and murder turns his life upside down.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Platform
subTitle: Vikram and Raju are brothers who work in a restaurant. When a conniving person frames Vikram in a murder case and separates them, circumstances lead Raju to a life of crime.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Mukt
subTitle: Suyambulingam, a school drop-out but an intelligent man, acquires knowledge by watching movies. When a dark incident seems to ruin his family, he uses all his wits to protect them.

title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Pighalta Aasman
subTitle: Arti, a businesswoman from Delhi, falls in love with Suraj, during her trip to settle a property dispute in Kashmir. However, things become complicated when Anuradha, her friend, also falls for him.

title: Main Inteqam Loonga
subTitle: A man discovers the truth behind his father's tragic demise and vows to avenge him, oblivious to the consequences that await him.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Baazigar
subTitle: A cold-blooded killer with a vendetta charms a businessman's elder daughter and then kills her in a way that would make it seem like a case of suicide. He then plots to destroy the rest of the family.

title: Bulandi
subTitle: Dharamraj Thakur, the head of a village, is highly respected by the villagers, However, his dignity is at stake when his younger brother, Arjun, is accused of raping a school teacher.

title: Sultanat
subTitle: Sultan, a brave warrior, tries to win the affections of Yasmin, a beautiful woman. However, his life turns upside down when his father is killed by a general, whom he swears revenge against.

title: Sultanat
subTitle: Sultan, a brave warrior, tries to win the affections of Yasmin, a beautiful woman. However, his life turns upside down when his father is killed by a general, whom he swears revenge against.

title: Main Hoon Chalbaaz
subTitle: Gudumba Shankar falls in love with Gowri and finds out that she is being forced to marry Kumar Swamy, a gangster. Shankar must find a way to stop him and save Gowri.

title: Barah Anna
subTitle: Three men inadvertently step into the world of crime by demanding small ransoms for kidnappings in order to improve their standard of living.

title: Nazar Ke Samne
subTitle: Jai, an unemployed drunk, gives false testimony that puts an innocent man in jail for murder. However, he later relents and tries to exonerate him by searching for the real killer.

title: Keemat: They Are Back
subTitle: Two crooks accidentally kill a man and decide to inform his parents about the bad news. However, once they meet the family, they end up lying to them.

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Sansar
subTitle: After finding out about her pregnancy, Uma decides to go and live with her parents. Upon her return, Uma learns about her broken family and decides to bring them back together.

title: Kohram
subTitle: Colonel Balbir Singh Sodhi assumes a disguise to unveil the true colours of Veer Bhadra Singh, a corrupt minister. Soon, Major Ajit teams up with him to execute the mission.

title: Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja
subTitle: Three friends, orphaned by an evil man, set out to take revenge for their father's murders. They are forced to navigate a complex web of deceit and stolen identities before they can reach their goal.
